            Usage: cmux resize-pane [--pane <id|ref|index>] [--workspace <id|ref|index>] [--window <id|ref|index>] [-L|-R|-U|-D] [--amount <n>]

            tmux-compatible pane resize command.

            Flags:
              --pane <id|ref|index>        Pane to resize (default: focused pane)
